# Offensive Security Intro

## Platform
TryHackMe

## Objective
Learn introductory concepts related to ethical hacking and offensive security.

## Topics Learned
- Ethical hacking
- Web exploitation basics
- Attack methodology
- Security testing mindset

## Key Takeaways
- Offensive security focuses on identifying weaknesses before attackers do.
- Curiosity and systematic thinking are important skills.
- Responsible disclosure and ethics are critical.

## Security Perspective
Understanding attacker techniques improves defensive security capabilities.